# Cloudflare headers. Filenames are un-hashed (app.css, data.js, …) and the site
# redeploys in place, so assets must always revalidate — a long max-age would serve
# stale CSS/JS/content to returning visitors after a deploy. no-cache = store but
# revalidate against the etag (cheap 304s when unchanged), so every deploy is live at once.
/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache
